<h3>Results</h3> 
<p>Just a week after launching the fundraising tool, we were thrilled to see our first users successfully adding fundraisers to their memorial pages. Some highlights:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Initial feedback from users was positive</li>
	<li>Fewer requests to customer support for help</li>
	<li>Fewer linkbanks to GoFundMe and external tools</li>
</ul>

<p>Though the initial launch was promising, more time was needed to understand long-term performance. Further iterations would focus on:</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Trust:</strong> Users wanted more reassurance about <em>how</em> we were making money. The funeral industry is riddled with predatory practices.</li>
	<li><strong>Tone:</strong> When it comes to talking about funerals and death, every person's comfort level is unique. </li>
</ul>


